# Sync Configuration for web-crawler skill
# This file documents how to synchronize this project to the Claude skills directory

## Synced Files
- src/ (complete source code)
- templates/ (HTML templates)
- Cargo.toml and Cargo.lock
- README.md
- SKILL.md (skill documentation)
- target/release/rcrawler → bin/rcrawler (binary)

## Sync Script Location
~/.claude/skills/web-crawler/sync.sh

## Usage
```bash
# From anywhere
sh ~/.claude/skills/web-crawler/sync.sh

# The script will:
# 1. Copy all files listed above
# 2. Rebuild binary if necessary
# 3. Copy binary to bin/
# 4. Test that everything works
```

## Notes
- Sync overwrites existing files in the skill directory
- Binary is automatically rebuilt if missing
- After sync, the skill is immediately usable
